.TP
\fB\-s\fR, \fB\-\-spaces\fR
break at spaces
.TP
\fB\-w\fR, \fB\-\-width\fR=\fIWIDTH\fR
use WIDTH columns instead of 80
.TP
\fB\-\-help\fR
display this help and exit
.TP
\fB\-\-version\fR
